messages.text: my computer is being jank
wat do u mean?
the screen is flickering
wat do u think it is?
not sure, but I’m pissed
sure it’ll be fine.
hope so, it was just getting good
wat was??
n this chat room
which one?
well, we’re just on FB, dogging Maddy
wat do you mean?
know that bitch from economics
quiet one that sits in the back?
ya, that freak
that’s not very nice. all she does is sit back there and not disturb anyone.
and stares, remember when she stared at me all class last Tuesday
no?! i didn’t even notice
well she did and it was creepy
so wat does this have to do with a chat room?
some of the girls in our school started this website
its an entire page dedicated to her just shitting on her
wat…
ya, its basically a chat room where anyone can come and comment and add to the discussion
the only rule is that u have to trash her as much as u can with each comment
that’s horrible…r u kidding?
nope, its wat she deserves
i dont get it, she hasn’t done anything.
by simply existing she’s done something
omg…its true.
how can everyone be so cruel?
cruel?! she’s a FREAK cindy
that doesn’t excuse u picking on her.
geez, i just txted u to tell u bout my computer, not get a lecture
carol, listen to me: im ur friend, but this isn’t right. at all.
u could get n2 serious trouble by parents or teachers if they found out.
plus u don’t know how this is making her feel!
o whateves, its just good fun
it’s the meanest thing ive ever seen!
well, i cant see anything still, computer still blacked out
maybe it’s for the better. i feel like i shoult say something…
wat do u mean say something? dont u dare ruin this
ruin bullying. gladly.
omg, it’s not bullying
r u kidding. Carol u said ‘she deserves to get run over by a truck then rot in the earth.’
thats the most absolute horrid thing 2 ever wish on someone
omg…i exaggerated a bit
u said ‘her face looks like the shit i took last night, not even plastic surgery could fix her.’
u have to admit that was kinda funny
this is just sick. frankly, im disappointed.
o big whoop, all the sudden uv become self-righteous on me
there. I commented.
WAT, WAT DID U SAY
i gave everyone a piece of my mind.
omg… u always find a way to spoil the fun
in this case, i did it with pleasure
ur such a-a
a wat? a bitch? Ooooo, wow, that really hurts.
wait, wat just happened
huh??
my computer screen is white
good, cant hurt anymore people
no, thats not the weirdest part…
sounded like some voice was speaking through the screen
wat voice?
idk…it was deep and scratchy
wat did it say?
my name
r u sure? thats just creepy.
THERE IT WAS AGAIN
wat did it say????
my name… twice
something weird is happening 2 the people on this chat site…
oh god… it told me to ‘come here’
only this time it whispered…
cindy help me… im scared…
no one is posting anymore.
my screen is slowly turning red now
wat is going on.
wait, someone posted a pic on the site.
oh no….
do u know donna??
of course, shes the one that started the site
well…she’s dead.
WAT!
she just posted a pic on the site of her hanging from a rope attached to the ceiling…
stop messin wit me
wish i was… omg, its so bad…im balling
that voice again… keeps calling me…telling me to come here
oh wow…
WAT?!?
more pics r popping up…
of wat?!?
more death…
everyone who commented on the site…
no, please, NO
wait, there’s something in each pic…
im not sure I wanna know
a shadow on the wall…
the voice is getting louder… my legs wont move…
it looks like some kind of man.
a large man, wide too. i cant really tell though.
Carol, u there? pics keep popping up.
hello?
CAROLINE!!
Maddy just posted… she found the cite.
saying something about revenge.
wait, u just posted a pic…
oh no…
